node.text:
Happy Birthday @henrygartland1 💜 @thehenrygartlandfoundation 

You were truly one-of-a-kind. Purple hair, don’t care! You lost your $500 grill on the way to the airport, but no grill needed to handle the handrails. One of the best on and off the board. You will be truly missed; we are all in this together! For those who might be struggling and can’t talk to anyone close to you PLEASE call the National suicide hotline 1-800-273-TALK. For additional resources and information check @thebenraemersfoundation
